Multitasking at its finest. After speaking with a few models today I felt like this needed to be shared. It should hopefully help everyone out in a photoshoot setting. The more pre-planning you can do beforehand will help cut out hours of wasted time on everyone's end. 
If you're like me and you're an extremely busy person, time is valuable and you don't want to waste it. Use these tips as guides. Be respectful of other's time. If you know you will need 15 hours of phone time then guess what...pay for it. Do not expect people to work for free just because that's how you run your life or it's just how your expectations are. 
Love you all so play nice please and be kind to each other.
